social_posts.post_text: Peace-signing and duck-facing my way through life #shitpostuntilshitcomestogether

Pleased to announce my first live music performance, happening next Wednesday 10pm - 11pm, 05/17/2023.

Will be performing songs from my existing discography as well as a ton of new unreleased tracks, with my talented brother and fellow musician @akinstrax on synth and guitar. 

A huge thank you to @vassarcollege and @viceweekly for making this happen. Crazy times!

No tickets, just come through and have fun ❤️ Doors at 9:30pm.

Photo design by my king and queen @beejamest and @chikazooo
Happy 4 year to my no. 1 ❤️‍🔥 This mf built different. Love you my angelic being
Feeling good feeling great. See y’all tomorrow!! 🦎 Much love again to my brother @akinstrax couldn’t do it without you ❤️

Vlog for my first ever live music performance now up and running on YT ❤️

@akinstrax absolutely demolished the set, can’t see future shows without you brother !! 

A huge shoutout again to @viceweekly and @vassarcollege for giving me the opportunity to step out of my shell, showing mad love even though I couldn’t hear myself and thought I sounded like shite half of the time. 

And lastly, thank you to those who have supported me in any shape or form over the years. You give me the confidence to keep it pushing. Gonna crawl back into my room now and finish the next body of work. Until then x
